  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Multicenter, observational, non-interventional registry designed to collect
      clinical data in Chinese patients who have received CUBICIN treatment under condition of
      actual usage in clinical practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
